text: Alana de la Garza (born June 18, 1976) is an American actress. She is known for her roles as Connie Rubirosa on the NBC television series Law & Order, Law & Order: LA, and in Law & Order: Special Victims Unit. She also played Marisol Delko-Caine on CSI: Miami. From 2016 to 2017, she was in Criminal Minds: Beyond Borders, playing Clara Seger. She also plays Isobel Castille on FBI and FBI: Most Wanted. De la Garza was born to a Mexican American father and an Irish American mother in Columbus, Ohio.
